snippet.title: Student Finds Hidden Devices in the College Library - Are they nefarious?
snippet.description:
A reddit user finds raspberry pi zeros hidden behind trash cans, vending machines and other places in the college library. We reverse engineer them and determine if they are malicious.

DirtyCOW video including "files" in Linux: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kEsshExn7aE
